## Starting the project

This is a Syfony 4 REST API, for now it provides authentication methods. Its make to be consume by [this project](https://github.com/falia15/react-redux-app).

## Initialiase project

``git clone https://github.com/falia15/symfony4-api.git``

`` cd symfony-4-api``

Create the .env file from the .env.exemple file, set DATABASE_URL and JWTKEY constance to your own setting.

Install dependencies
`` composer install``

Create Database
``php bin/console doctrine:database:create``

Make and execute migration
``php bin/console make:migration``
``php bin/console doctrine:migrations:migrate``

Run server
``php bin/console server:run``
